<sub>m</sub> = &#x02212;24 mV. It is typical of the behavior of the model for small Na<sup>+</sup> window current, and it contains four regions.</p><fig id="pcbi-0030156-g002" position="float"><label>Figure 2</label><caption><title>Responses of the Model Neuron to Noiseless Current Steps for Small Na<sup>+</sup> Window Current (<italic>&#x003b8;</italic>
<sub>m</sub> = &#x02212;24 mV)</title><p>(A) The phase diagram of the model neuron in the <italic>I</italic>
