<sub>m</sub> = &#x02212;24 mV, <italic>g</italic>
<sub>d</sub> = 1.8 mS/cm<sup>2</sup>, <italic>I</italic>
<sub>app</sub> = 4.2 &#x003bc;A/cm<sup>2</sup>.</p><p>(C) Delayed tonic firing for <italic>&#x003b8;</italic>
